snippet.title: Release Date Reveal | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
#Overwatch2 arrives October 4 as an always-on, always-evolving, free to play experience. Team up in a new 5v5 PvP experience, featuring new and reworked heroes, new maps and modes, and more.

Learn more about the newest tank hero to join the roster: Junker Queen, Overwatch 2's live service model and seasonal content plan during the Overwatch 2 Reveal Event livestream June 16 at 10 AM PT.

Follow #Overwatch2 for the latest news:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playoverwatch
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@overwatch
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/playoverwatch 
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/playoverwatch
